title:
The Structural and Magnetic ordering in
  $La{}_{0.5-x}Nd_{x}Ca_{0.5}MnO_{3}$ (0.1 \ensuremath{\le} x \ensuremath{\le}
  0.5) Manganites

description:
Comment: RUB preprint 52/93, 39p. Two figures (out of four) included at the
  end as uudecoded poscript file. Two other figures can be sent upon request:
  E-mail to diakonov@lnpi.spb.su

Comment: LaTeX, 17 pages, one uuencoded figure, CALT-68-1904, {Some editorial
  changes as suggested by an anonymous referee, one figure added, to appear in
  Phys. Rev. D Rapid Comm.}

  The analogue of the string equation which specifies the partition function of
$c=1$ string with a compactification radius $\beta \in \mbox{$\bf{Z}$}_{\geq 1}
$ is described in the framework of the Toda lattice hierarchy.
